{"tid":2111861,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［確認書］黃之鋒：由衷希望「簽就一齊簽，唔簽就一齊唔簽」簽署與否不應淪為比拼立場的辯題","createTime":"2020-07-17T00:50:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T02:30:13.000Z","uid":48083,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"00434e91a20d4295a1f56bb4581bc5ae2104ab1c","tid":2111861,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T00:50:47.000Z","msg":"黃之鋒 Joshua Wong<br />\n【關於確認書：簽署與否不應淪為民主派互相比拼立場的辯題】<br />\n<br />\n距離立法會選舉提名期開始尚餘兩天時間，目前「國安法」三字至今仍不存在於確認書當中。當然，政權如此瘋狂，仍不能排除確認書內文在提名期前一天，突然變本加厲，但以下一切觀點陳述，均以確認書內文維持現有版本為前提。<br />\n<br />\n回顧過去四年的選舉，簽署確認書能夠入閘的，有為數不少素人。簽署確認書後仍被取消資格的，則有我和梁天琦等人。不簽署確認書也能入閘的，就有公民黨和人民力量。至於拒簽確認書後被取消資格的，便有陳浩天。由此可見，政權過去取消任何政治人物的參選資格與否，其實並不取決於該人有否簽署確認書。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，政治人物的抗爭意志能否彰顯，其實並不在於簽署確認書的環節，正如無人會因梁天琦曾簽確認書，而質疑他的抗爭意志；而選民亦已透過初選，授權誰人背負民意參與往後議會抗爭，過去一年積極投入反送中運動的候選人，亦確實以高票當選。<br />\n<br />\n那，既然確認書一直並非用作DQ參選人的衡量指標，亦非有效評估政治人物有否抱持抗爭意志，到底在2020年的香港，對中共來說，仍有甚麼作用？正如我參與草擬的聲明提到「北京早已為破壞我們團結與互信設下陷阱」，而這陷阱就是確認書。<br />\n<br />\n在我而言，如選舉論壇所述，當然堅拒簽署任何支持國安法的文件。不過，簽不簽署至今仍未有國安法字眼的確認書，漸成所有候選人會見記者時，必定要回應的必答題。簽確認書與否，在選舉期間，容易被視作比拼激進取態的做法，這點尚可理解；但我擔心的是，即使初選過後，簽不簽署這種爭拗仍成為民主派互相指責的機會（這經已發生）。<br />\n<br />\n昨天，我與十多位朋友表明「就著未來有關文件簽署的取態，我們將會約見泛民初選人作磋商，期望整個民主陣營能團結一致，毋負選民期望」。各人在聲明內容裡未有交待個人想法，原意是希望先跟民主派同路人討論，方共同交待正式立場。<br />\n<br />\n同日晚上，已有不只一位初選參與者，當中更包括政黨領袖，在社交媒體表明拒簽確認書。我想，表明立場是可以理解的，但若在字裡行間暗批其他會簽署確認書的候選人，爭論有否尊嚴，在初選過後仍對同路人抱有敵視態度者，並不會是廣大支持者樂見。<br />\n<br />\n正因如此，我個人由衷希望，「簽就一齊簽，唔簽就一齊唔簽」。無論最後能否達成共識，我也希望在初選過後，各陣營放下分歧並非淪為空談。簽署與否不會成為遭到同路人攻擊的話題，如《抗爭派立法會參選人立場聲明：同行，是我們唯一選擇。》（ <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/joshuawongchifung/photos/a.564294826996363\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjoshuawongchifung%2Fphotos%2Fa.564294826996363&d=q%2BUwj3SihaKoadPXZHTFaVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=9f805ed0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/joshuawongchifung/photos/a.564294826996363</a> ）的聲明所言 &mdash;&mdash; 「民主陣營參選人的真正抉擇，不只拘泥於簽署與否，而是在於同行抑或分道」。<br />\n<br />\n哩篇野寫得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c27a6b451e75da56eef1d064652f20a57c5932cc","tid":2111861,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T01:26:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0a58b2b731aff4b5e1c145c587bc953ece06942","tid":2111861,"uid":173326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T01:28:53.000Z","msg":"比拼激進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔簽好激進咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"626103bf06d5349f6eab1e3ffc7a2218e9101b80","tid":2111861,"uid":227788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T01:30:38.000Z","msg":"齊上齊落"},{"pid":"b929c964e11112b8c3c3ccf54067b31d134a6b24","tid":2111861,"uid":227788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T01:30:54.000Z","msg":"齊上齊落"},{"pid":"d7900f8bd8abd3b6d3cbc3589f85739bcf910d4a","tid":2111861,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T01:31:40.000Z","msg":"［重要］信報：泛民抗爭派齊上落? 確認書成試金石<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2111880\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2111880</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f7a38692762f9407bc79399063bcb6031a00025d","tid":2111861,"uid":94241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T01:31:44.000Z","msg":"公民黨同民主黨都好似表左態唔簽了？<br />\n仲有邊個未表態？"},{"pid":"0bdf78d39c51b28dadaa184afc56bc72c7ced38c","tid":2111861,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7a38692762f9407bc79399063bcb6031a00025d","tid":2111861,"uid":94241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T01:31:44.000Z","msg":"公民黨同民主黨都好似表左態唔簽了？<br />\n仲有邊個未表態？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T01:32:57.000Z","msg":"信報既風：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有參與會議的人士形容，部分出線的素人有意簽署確認書，認為此做法並無不妥，亦不擔心遭外界扭曲成支持《港區國安法》，但有出席者直言動筆與否是「原則問題」，不能貿然簽署。"},{"pid":"641b2c8ddd77abfad2fd333d89e45912285e1597","tid":2111861,"uid":129134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T01:33:07.000Z","msg":"各參選人在論壇上被問到確認書若加入支持國安法條文，會否因為入閘而簽署。<strong>黃之鋒率先指，他忠誠反對國安法，故不會簽署任何支持國安法的文件</strong>，又建議民主派候選人一同拒簽確認書，增加政權DQ參選人的成本：「堅定嘅抵抗意志係香港需要見到，而今次初選投票亦都係讓政權知道香港人未投降。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7655a43709a5c8c24109fd4f17d28fb26d374af","tid":2111861,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T01:37:12.000Z","msg":"簽左一定係鬼<br />\n<br />\n不平等條約都簽得 第日屎都食得"},{"pid":"aa1081ec3c21f3351fcb355a5005c3895da6bfe2","tid":2111861,"uid":66221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b7655a43709a5c8c24109fd4f17d28fb26d374af","tid":2111861,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T01:37:12.000Z","msg":"簽左一定係鬼<br />\n<br />\n不平等條約都簽得 第日屎都食得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T01:43:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CU0aCW1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCU0aCW1.png&h=aef4568d&s={SIZE}\" />舊屎你自己食返，仲有紅報果啲乜人士形容，專家透露又咪係作故仔，叫佢哋早少少出聲澄清簽唔簽就夠啦"},{"pid":"3ab606adfe210ca1400e1cda60bf82972cd7af27","tid":2111861,"uid":71564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T02:29:10.000Z","msg":"佢想保覺得簽無問題個班？<br />\n不過佢地唔係開記招叫自己做抗爭派咩<br />\n咁樣唔係話依家個班係妥協派咩<br />\n<br />\n一時一樣好難捉摸<br />\n不如傾掂數先出聲<br />\n依家左右不是人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9222efceaa4337c657fe9159479c922f064e1052","tid":2111861,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T02:30:13.000Z","msg":"最好全部唔好簽 全部DQ晒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}